{"tid":1588704,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（建議）我唔同意玩國旗係高效益","createTime":"2019-09-23T02:44:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T03:16:52.000Z","uid":198258,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4d703784e3ad86e1b4e02203dd473385357d80eb","tid":1588704,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:44:12.000Z","msg":"頭盔：睇到有人玩國旗內心會微笑<br />\n但係爽完都要正視個影響，唔可以阿Q精神。<br />\n<br />\n首先玩國旗絕對唔係低成本，有手足極速被拉，成本仲高過你去拆欄杆。<br />\n<br />\n你話激到中共？真心？<br />\n<br />\n我係中共見到你玩旗開心到忍唔住笑。<br />\n<br />\n大家回憶番運動一開始共匪嘅反應，佢係十分地低調，出下聲話支持政府，然後重點打壓消息。<br />\n顯然就係怕上面啲人有樣學樣。<br />\n<br />\n依家呢？驚死有人唔知香港玩佢支旗咁大大力揚出去，你話咁樣係落佢面？你比人落面嘅時候會大大聲同其他人講？<br />\n<br />\n星星之火就講得多，咁到底星火係點樣點起？<br />\n：我係一個大陸人，知道左香港有勁嘅示威，第一反應當然係問點解會咁。然後知道左香港人打死都唔信任中國法治，仲知道左有中共撐腰嘅警暴有幾可怕。開始諗點解黨一定就等於中國？<br />\n咁樣就係一朵星火。<br />\n<br />\n可惜依家個情況係，大陸人覺得香港示威係反中國，好嬲，完。<span style=\"color: red;\">加劇左反政府就係反中國呢個思想</span>，幫助中共鞏固地位。<br />\n<br />\n咁中共仲嬲啲咩？佢冇左塊布，真係一塊布，就阻斷左星火北上，仲勁過防火牆。你係中共你嬲得落？<br />\n<br />\n敵人反對的就要擁護呢句唔夠準，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">敵人害怕的就越要做</span></span><br />\n<br />\n諗番中共一開始最怕咩，係怕啲人開始思考點解黨會等於國。<br />\n所以，我嘅睇法係採用品聰內地同路人嘅建議，於929/101全力推動四星紅旗/五星平等紅旗，同赤納粹旗有異曲同工之妙。<br />\n<br />\n呢個就係大家想要嘅對準政權，對準主線。<br />\n當中共提都唔政提嘅時候，就真係佢驚嘅時候。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTLDR:玩五星平等旗更有殺傷力<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">終極頭盔：以上評論只針對內地戰線。國際上的話當然冇咩所謂，話唔定真係燒燒下助攻埋外國反中國霸權風氣，我睇好哈薩克咖</span>"},{"pid":"7b24c1b0ad8f2bc89489ec85f4563ef1a92849cb","tid":1588704,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:44:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"a8024014e4a955ab1cd1158354ce84ccabe1d83e","tid":1588704,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:47:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e57b9ceb4bdac56f993ff55aac9ee375c1b1850","tid":1588704,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:47:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb9c1ec97739693462c5307eb4b5845f20c8a11b","tid":1588704,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:47:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28a939980c5a555a86f94b1541c0d9189c2c62fb","tid":1588704,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:48:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ed7e3f6516e41add94c6417e39272ea48fd6709","tid":1588704,"uid":59536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:48:38.000Z","msg":"愛國反共係最好 <br />\n不過大家都唔想做中國人"},{"pid":"9a06a014ad2a25be7a9f5be5445ed7de866d1ef2","tid":1588704,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2ed7e3f6516e41add94c6417e39272ea48fd6709","tid":1588704,"uid":59536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:48:38.000Z","msg":"愛國反共係最好 <br />\n不過大家都唔想做中國人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:50:08.000Z","msg":"忍下姐，冇話要認嘅，<br />\n比上面啲人搞臭晒個朵，唔想做係正常"},{"pid":"736fd69bab6e3447db7775061f7bdf32f8b9ed44","tid":1588704,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:50:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99dc0385cfbc989b52b18881aceb1a0281fce32f","tid":1588704,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:50:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f226aa97faca4ea8b9957d5b0da7f64a0f19b22d","tid":1588704,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:51:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9196186c529de3191ae98cf05699420f7fe5450","tid":1588704,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:51:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"241f37192baaa4566e1d562d435ca1e0f4955935","tid":1588704,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:51:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68483296b07d121ebe18dc7cdcb71beab89e5bf6","tid":1588704,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:51:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"906eb3ee2d85b1965e6fafbe255a1b2edbd4d7dc","tid":1588704,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:53:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c8f6ee458a235535b0c1e675f316736ab91b0c4","tid":1588704,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:53:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"740922665dafc0eec60343a05a8f3553cc305bc9","tid":1588704,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:53:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01a6a057168a073f0e54afe8e8a0fb4eb9a6076a","tid":1588704,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:53:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b3592613bb5f380c79504fde77a8fc23484fc69","tid":1588704,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:53:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2dc41aabc5c990c51a45985a28a4f65845ad416","tid":1588704,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T02:54:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6981f1326fd3cb9da266dcf7de279bc6e860a0d","tid":1588704,"uid":140793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T03:16:52.000Z","msg":"黨旗都唔錯㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}